ed together with the tracker's ability\nto correctly recognize them. The analysis is supported by Monte Carlo\nsimulations using Geant4 and Garfield++ packages. Finally, the preliminary\nresults from the 114In spectrum study are presented.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 21 Aug 2022 21:48:16 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-09-21"}
