ach provides a basis for\nunderstanding and discovering various morphological changes in photochromic\ncrystals and similar systems.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 22 Aug 2022 02:09:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-02-22"}
