l dynamics mixes torpidly while the\nproposed dynamics on the modified landscape mixes rapidly with polynomial\ndependence on both $\\beta$ and $N$ and find the approximate ground state\nprovably in $\\mathcal{O}(N^4)$ time. This paper highlights a novel use of the\ngeometry and structure of the landscape to the design of accelerated samplers\nor optimizers.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 22 Aug 2022 04:42:09 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-08-23"}
